          "email": "kbanka.os@gmail.com",
          "username": "kbanka"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-10-31 07:35:41.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> This change provides minimal improvement in build time (average\n > build time is lower on average from 18 to 16 minutes). This is\n > mainly because KUD installation doesn't rely much on compute power\n > and doesn't contain many parallel operations executed (in\n > single-node deployment). This can, however help when CI will be\n > enriched by providing currently missing verification steps, that\n > may be more affected by node capabilities (tests include\n > compilation of go code, deployments of k8s resources).\n\nIt's also worth noting, that quite big part of verification time is spent on waiting for jenkins slave to appear, that basically cannot be solved by jobs/gerrit/code improvements",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
